<h2 id="the-power-of-purpose">The Power of Purpose</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Purpose diminishes distractions.</li>
  <li>Purpose pushes you through the pain.</li>
  <li>Purpose empowers you to please God.</li>
</ol>

